Also, please, change your program to

package main

import (
	"net/http"
	"fmt"
)

func main() {
	fmt.Println("Hello")
	resp, err := http.Get("http://google.com")
	
	fmt.Println(resp)
	fmt.Println(err)
}

and tell us, if you could see "Hello" printed before your program crashes or not. Thank
you.
